init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You can’t escape as you’re glued to your seat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After it’s done you are taken forward to live your next life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It allows us to experience all the different roles we can play.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It allows us to be a parent, to be a child, to be an animal or plant.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Some people believe that reincarnation is like going from one room into another, and then you decide if you want to go back to the original

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We also get to choose our next life, including the place where we will live and who we will be.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Whatever your belief is, reincarnation allows us to experience the many different roles we can play.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: What is it like to be a ghost?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: To be a ghost is to be in purgatory.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But it is not a painful experience, it is just very quiet and calm.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is almost like being in suspended animation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There is no time, there are no seasons, there is no physical pain.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We are social creatures, and we feel safe in our own realm.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: To move on from the physical body is very challenging for many people.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are used to their physical body.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is a safe feeling for a human.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: when we die and move on, we go to a better place.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: To many people, the afterlife is better than this Earth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Heaven is a wonderful place to be.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is a place where there is no pain, suffering, or any other negative experience.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is a place where we can live forever with the people who are most important to us.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world has so many different religions, and humans have a hard time to putting their faith into one set of beliefs.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: what you want to believe in.
